channel.description: hey i downloaded JDK 6u1 but wen i go to compile it says u do not have jdk 6.0... well i cant get 6.0 its outadate now.... idk what to do to get it to compile can someone help mee?

item.title: My compiler... and jdk
item.dc:creator: @us_sniper04 us sniper04
item.description:
@us_sniper04 wrote:

ok go into your compiler and find this at the very top of the compiler

@echo off if exist "C:\Program Files (x86)\" set programfiles=C:\Program Files (x86) set pro=%programfiles%\Java\jdk1.5.0 set pro2=%programfiles%\Java\jdk1.6.0

then change it to

@echo off if exist "C:\Program Files (x86)\" set programfiles=C:\Program Files (x86) set pro=%programfiles%\Java\jdk1.5.0 set pro2=%programfiles%\Java\jdk1.6.0_01
